#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn22.131"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn22.131:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 22 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 22 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.131:0.2"
msgid "13. Avijjāvagga "
msgstr "13. Ignorance "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn22.131:0.3"
msgid "131. Samudayasutta "
msgstr "131. Origin "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn22.131:1.1"
msgid "Bārāṇasiyaṃ viharanti isipatane migadāye … pe … "
msgstr "At Benares. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.131:1.2"
msgid "“‘avijjā, avijjā’ti, āvuso sāriputta, vuccati. "
msgstr "“Reverend Sāriputta, they speak of this thing called ‘ignorance’. "

msgctxt "sn22.131:1.3"
msgid "Katamā nu kho, āvuso, avijjā; "
msgstr "What is ignorance? "

msgctxt "sn22.131:1.4"
msgid "kittāvatā ca avijjāgato hotī”ti? "
msgstr "And how is an ignorant person defined?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn22.131:2.1"
msgid "“Idhāvuso, assutavā puthujjano rūpassa samudayañca atthaṅgamañca assādañca ādīnavañca nissaraṇañca yathābhūtaṃ nappajānāti. "
msgstr "“Reverend, an uneducated ordinary person doesn’t truly understand the origin, the ending, the gratification, the drawback, and the escape when it comes to form, "

msgctxt "sn22.131:2.2"
msgid "Vedanāya … pe … "
msgstr "feeling, "

msgctxt "sn22.131:2.3"
msgid "saññāya … "
msgstr "perception, "

msgctxt "sn22.131:2.4"
msgid "saṅkhārānaṃ … "
msgstr "choices, "

msgctxt "sn22.131:2.5"
msgid "viññāṇassa samudayañca atthaṅgamañca assādañca ādīnavañca nissaraṇañca yathābhūtaṃ nappajānāti. "
msgstr "and consciousness. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.131:2.6"
msgid "Ayaṃ vuccatāvuso, avijjā; "
msgstr "This is called ignorance. "

msgctxt "sn22.131:2.7"
msgid "ettāvatā ca avijjāgato hotī”ti. "
msgstr "And this is how an ignorant person is defined.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn22.131:2.8"
msgid "Chaṭṭhaṃ. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
